msgid "Color calibration"
msgstr "Calibration des couleurs"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/news/color-controls-finally-correct/index.md:258
#, no-wrap
msgid "In _color calibration_, the 3 tabs _R_, _G_, and _B_ have been merged into the same _mixer_ tab, which now fits entirely vertically. Same for _brightness_, _colorfulness_ and _B&W_ which are now merged into _outputs_.\n"
msgstr "Dans _calibration des couleurs_, les 3 onglets _R_, _G_ et _B_ ont été fusionnés dans le même onglet _mélangeur_, qui tient désormais entièrement verticalement. Il en va de même pour _luminosité_, _coloration_ et _N&B_ qui sont maintenant fusionnés dans _sorties_.\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/news/color-controls-finally-correct/index.md:260
#, no-wrap
msgid "The _mixer_ tab has now 2 alternative GUI modes, in addition of the typical one (now dubbed _complete_) ;\n"
msgstr "L'onglet _mélangeur_ a désormais 2 modes d'interface alternatifs, en plus du mode habituel (désormais baptisé _complet_) ;\n"

# TRANSLATOR Claude
#. type: Plain text
#: content/news/color-controls-finally-correct/index.md:266
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{{% gallery cols=3 %}}\n"
"{{< figure src=\"color-calibration-complete.jpg\" caption=\"Complete mode\" />}}\n"
"{{< figure src=\"color-calibration-simple.jpg\" caption=\"Simple mode\" />}}\n"
"{{< figure src=\"color-calibration-primaries.jpg\" caption=\"Primaries\" />}}\n"
