msgid "I implemented a [topological sorting algorithm](https://github.com/aurelienpierreeng/ansel/blob/2a84c20769742d370aac8623238d65bccaa97655/src/common/topological_sort.c) in C. Or more accurately, ChatGPT did and I checked it (more on that below). 304 lines of code, which, for C, is very few.\n"
