msgstr "[^4] : HACKMAN, J. Richard. Leading teams: Setting the stage for great performances. Harvard Business Press, 2002. [URL](https://books.google.fr/books?id=snfoCQAAQBAJ&lpg=PR5&ots=SCn-vzTdUf&dq=J.%20Richard%20Hackman%20(Harvard%2C%202002)&lr&hl=fr&pg=PR8#v=onepage&q=J.%20Richard%20Hackman%20(Harvard,%202002)&f=false)"

# TRANSLATOR ChatGPT
#. type: Link reference
#: content/contribute/democracy.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "[^5]: WHEELAN, Susan A. Group size, group development, and group productivity. Small group research, 2009, vol. 40, no 2, p. 247-262. [URL](https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1177/1046496408328703)"
msgstr "[^5] : WHEELAN, Susan A. Group size, group development, and group productivity. Small group research, 2009, vol. 40, no 2, p. 247-262. [URL](https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/abs/10.1177/1046496408328703)"

